{"tid":2088121,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"關於第38條 忽然間諗到啲嘢","createTime":"2020-07-01T03:54:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-01T04:52:16.000Z","uid":310446,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"0c8089882d3697b1edcdb7f745c040f8a5a36a25","tid":2088121,"uid":310446,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T03:54:47.000Z","msg":"國安法第38條係直外國公民只要行為涉及分裂國家或者有做任何違反國安法嘅行為 一入香港就拉得<br />\n加上60條可以無限擴大國安在港權力<br />\n<br />\n問題黎喇<br />\n照佢咁講 換言之啫係任何一個有同香港訂引渡協議嘅國家<br />\n只要國安出聲就可以用38條拉人?<br />\n<br />\n咁啫係話唔埋你喺地球上任何一個角落 只要係同中國或者香港有引渡條約嘅國家 你都有可能被送中<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53ed203c5724d85d66b4e079d939bbc0fbaa7b13","tid":2088121,"uid":18948,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T03:55:28.000Z","msg":"要喺對方國家都有犯法，先至有雙重犯罪嘅原則"},{"pid":"65d817ca44bf4db1465d35549a2b36bd9a3c3f92","tid":2088121,"uid":15812,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T03:55:57.000Z","msg":"使咩引渡<br />\n直接係外國拉你然後就地正法<br />\n國安法係大晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9304ad3cbdef2bc9bcad834b92c101267b4bbd02","tid":2088121,"uid":289946,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T03:56:01.000Z","msg":"人地自由世界國家唔會咁做啦，你去北韓就會"},{"pid":"1652337223c36731787877ae3b77fe7f21501be5","tid":2088121,"uid":323443,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T03:58:22.000Z","msg":"桂敏海就係咁"},{"pid":"b4e9738a99b13fb689cde5027f87e5b28f5abe35","tid":2088121,"uid":146030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T04:00:10.000Z","msg":"政治罪唔引渡"},{"pid":"3327c75df894b436ed219e642a21e33102b09076","tid":2088121,"uid":56326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T04:01:24.000Z","msg":"又冇人叫你去白俄羅斯旅行嘅"},{"pid":"6211643331f698813951e5cccc092afdd739020a","tid":2088121,"uid":41308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T04:01:25.000Z","msg":"咁咪取消引渡協議law<